  • Method Details

    • accessRoom

      public Room accessRoom(String roomNumber)
      This method uses the XmlReader to get the file directories for the three Rooms of each level. If another parameter than Room1, Room2 or Room3 is provided, an IllegalStateException will be thrown.
      Parameters:
      roomNumber - The Room's number you try to access.
      Returns:
      the Room property value based on the roomNumber parameter.
